<section class="hero">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <p class="kicker reveal-up">Partner embed</p>
    <h1 class="reveal-up">Drop transfer booking<br>onto your site.</h1>
    <p class="lead reveal-up">Ready iframe widget with your preferred rate. Requests reach our manager tagged with your partner ID.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container container--narrow prose">
    <h2>How to onboard</h2>
    <ol class="checklist">
      <li><strong>Reach out</strong> — receive a unique <code>partner_id</code>.</li>
      <li><strong>Paste the snippet</strong> on your site.</li>
      <li><strong>Requests arrive</strong> tagged with your <code>partner_id</code> — monthly report included.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 3rem;">HTML snippet</h2>
    <p class="muted small">Replace <code>YOUR_PARTNER_ID</code> with the ID you received.</p>
    <div class="code-block">
      <button type="button" class="copy-btn copy-btn--code" data-copy='&lt;iframe src="https://morrison-transfer.com/widget/?partner=YOUR_PARTNER_ID" width="100%" height="640" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" title="Morrison Premium Transfer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;' data-copy-label="Copy" data-copied-label="Copied"><span class="copy-icon">⎘</span> Copy</button>
<pre><code>&lt;iframe
  src="https://morrison-transfer.com/widget/?partner=YOUR_PARTNER_ID"
  width="100%" height="640"
  frameborder="0" loading="lazy"
  title="Morrison Premium Transfer"&gt;
&lt;/iframe&gt;</code></pre>
    </div>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 3rem;">Inside the widget</h2>
    <ul class="checklist">
      <li>Route calculator</li>
      <li>Booking brief (address, date, passengers)</li>
      <li>Submit via WhatsApp to your manager</li>
      <li>Branding: your logo at top of the widget (by arrangement)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 3rem;">Parameters</h2>
    <ul class="checklist">
      <li><code>?partner=ID</code> — required</li>
      <li><code>&theme=dark</code> — dark theme</li>
      <li><code>&lang=pt</code> — default language</li>
      <li><code>&from=GRU</code> — prefill origin</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="muted small" style="margin-top: 2rem; padding-top: 1.4rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--line);">
      Embed widget is in pilot. To get a <code>partner_id</code> now — message us on WhatsApp, activated in one day.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-strip">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h2>Request a partner_id?</h2>
    <div class="cta-strip-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-dark btn-arrow" href="{{ site.contacts.whatsappUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a>
